<plot>The Fallen Faithful houses the epic theme of good versus evil deep within one character. Our hero Moran, a religious man, searching for a profound and meaningful connection with God. He is also a man of violence, a hired killer. Riddled with inner turmoil, Moran tries to live his life serving two master, Asa, a loan shark and a despicable human being, and the Lord. He struggles to gain the courage to leave his life of sin behind without becoming a victim himself.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?556666</url></doc>
